{
  "texts": [
    "First, we will review aspects of AI to help familiarize readers with basic concepts, especially in the context of clinical genetics.",
    "Second, we will briefly review previous, current, and emerging applications of AI in clinical genetics.",
    "While this review is not meant to be systematic or comprehensive (and will focus on the most recent \"game-changing\" AI developments), it may nonetheless be useful to readers who, like all of us, are constantly bombarded with information about AI, but who may feel less knowledgeable about the underlying methods, applications, and considerations.",
    "At the same time, this review will touch on some challenging and controversial questions regarding AI in clinical genetics.",
    "As a side note, readers may well disagree with many of the points and opinions in this review article."
  ]
}